        <item>
            <title>Sigma BF 全片幅無反相機正式亮相，鋁合金一體成型外殼、支援 6K 錄影 + L-Log</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:59:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sigma]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sigma BF]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293659</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sigma 發表全新 BF 全片幅無反相機，以極簡設計為核心，融合 2,460 萬像素感光元件、內置 230GB 儲存空間和 6K 錄影功能，為攝影師帶來回歸本源的純粹體驗。機身採用鋁合金一體成型，由單塊鋁材經過長達 7 小時精雕細琢，造就堅固耐用的機殼。Sigma 冀望透過簡約的操作介面及觸覺反饋系統，讓使用者在拍攝過程中得心應手、遊刃有餘。BF 將於 2025 年 4 月正式發售，備有黑色與銀色兩種機身顏色選擇，建議售價為 1,999 美元（約港幣 HK$15,600）。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003-657x580.jpeg" alt="" width="657" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003-657x580.jpeg 657w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 657px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身採用鋁合金一體成型，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>BF 配備 2,460 萬像素全片幅背照式 CMOS 感光元件，提供高解析度及寬廣動態範圍，讓影像細節盡收眼底。自動對焦系統結合相位檢測與對比檢測技術，支援人像與動物主體追蹤，即使面對瞬息萬變的拍攝場景，亦能迅速對焦，捕捉精彩剎那。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>影片拍攝方面，BF 可錄製 6K 高畫質影片，並支援 L-Log 設定，滿足專業用戶在後期調色上的需求，無論用於紀錄片創作或商業攝影，皆能表現出色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>操作體驗方面，BF 延續極簡美學，全機僅設三個按鈕、一個轉盤及快門鍵，將複雜操作簡化至最直觀層面。用家可以利用輕觸式熒幕調整體主要拍攝參數如快門速度、光圈、ISO 感光度、曝光補償及色彩模式，減少繁瑣步驟，讓用戶專注於構圖與創作。BF 亦是首款在撥盤與按鈕中引入觸覺反饋技術的無反相機，操作時能提供恰到好處的震動回應，使拍攝體驗如虎添翼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934-694x343.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934-694x343.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934.jpg 1218w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utkFqcOnKsI&amp;ab_channel=SIGMAAmerica">Sigma America@Youtube</a><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293663" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>儲存能力同樣令人稱道。BF 具有 230GB 儲存空間，足以儲存逾 14,000 張 JPEG 圖片、4,300 張未壓縮 RAW 圖片或約 2.5 小時最高畫質影片。用家可以利用 USB-C 接口充電、傳輸資料，無論是戶外拍攝或日常應用，皆方便快捷，讓創作過程無後顧之憂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293664" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05-674x580.jpg" alt="" width="674" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05-674x580.jpg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05.jpg 1045w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 674px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07-674x580.jpg" alt="" width="674" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07-674x580.jpg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07.jpg 1045w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 674px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utkFqcOnKsI">Sigma America@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a>、<a href="https://petapixel.com/2025/02/23/the-sigma-bf-is-a-radically-simple-24-6mp-full-frame-compact-camera/">Peta Pixel</a>、<a href="https://www.dpreview.com/news/1398165547/sigma-bf-a-mirrorless-camera-unlike-anything-you-ve-seen">DP Review</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/">Sigma BF 全片幅無反相機正式亮相，鋁合金一體成型外殼、支援 6K 錄影 + L-Log</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
